## Look up an Existing Pg Resource {#look-up}

Get an existing Pg resource's state with the given name, ID, and optional extra properties used to qualify the lookup.

        <span class="property-type"><a href="https://docs.python.org/3/library/stdtypes.html">bool</a></span>
    </dt>
    <dd>{{% md %}}Prevent service from being deleted. It is recommended to have this enabled for all services.
{{% /md %}}</dd>

</dl>
{{% /choosable %}}
